name: Virile Reality
description:
If you'd like to buy me a beer or coffee! 🍺☕

Virile Reality V2

  • Rebuilt from the ground up!

  • Now with flaccid penises (prompt for "flaccid penis")

New merges:

  • A-Zovya Photoreal

  • Unstable Homoerotic Diffusion (UHD)

  • SofteePee Lora (Own creation, not available as a standalone yet)

  • BetterCocks Flaccid

  • Instant photo 拍立得/Polaroid LoRA

My settings (A1111):

  • Sampling Method: DPM++ SDE Karras

  • Sampling Steps: 28

  • Hires. fix On

  • Upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+

  • Hires Steps: 14

  • Denoising Strength: 0.5

  • Upscale: 1.75

  • Width: 512

  • Height: 768

  • CFG Scale: 8


I also highly recommend using After Detailer for faces, using the "mediapipe_face_full" model with the "Restore faces after Adetailer" option enabled.

Hope you enjoy!

This model is my second merge and has been fine-tuned in order to produce convincing and realistic male-focused gens without the need for Loras, even with simple prompts.

This model is built upon my previous merge, Virile Fusion, however it is not a replacement and only aims at offering a more realistic style, which could not be achieved by VF.

In the end, whichever model you decide to use is a matter of preference.

Models included in the merge are:

  • Virile Fusion

  • Realistic Vision V2.0

  • ICBINP - "I Can't Believe It's Not Photography"

  • Juggernaut

Loras included in the merge are:

  • Penis LoRA

  • Tgirls

While the model has been crafted to be male-centric, it also allows for the generation of other types of characters (including females) as well as landscapes, or objects.

Recommended settings for good gens (Automatic1111):

  • Sampling Method: DPM++ SDE Karras

  • Sampling Steps: 22

  • Hires. fix On

  • Upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+

  • Hires Steps: 10

  • Denoising Strength: 0.5

  • Upscale: 1.7

  • Width: 512

  • Height: 768

  • CFG Scale: 6

I also highly recommend using After Detailer for faces, using the "mediapipe_face_mesh" model.

I did not bake any VAE into the model and would advise to use the following one: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

I would also like to mention and thank the Unstable Diffusion Discord Server's #men-only community who helped me learn a lot. Some of the gens done with the model include their prompts.
